{"tid":1634574,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Joker邊個好? 積尼高遜、希夫烈達、華堅菲獵斯","createTime":"2019-10-07T08:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T14:34:28.000Z","uid":188282,"like":4,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"9dac1570572fc6bdc01b61166c943ab271536633","tid":1634574,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"其實唔駛分駛分高低<br />\n而係呢三個演員表現左三種唔同嘅可能性<br />\n積尼係笛子大魔王<br />\n希夫烈達係第一次嚟地球嘅比達(只限呢個時期)<br />\n華堅菲獵斯係菲利<br />\n<br />\n如果積尼將小丑演到魔王級<br />\n希夫烈達就係充滿毀滅性，就好似條拉到就嚟斷嘅橡筋咁。<br />\n果陣睇完希夫烈達，你會諗以後冇人超越倒佢啦。<br />\n點知華堅菲獵斯話你知，你係唔駛超越佢 而係要將小丑帶去另種形態境界，唔係更高或更低而係第二種唔同嘅方向。<br />\n<br />\n好勁。多謝呢三位演員。<br />\n<br />\nbtw.<br />\n仲想傾吓今次嘅留白位。<br />\n1，呢個小丑係咪Batman果個?<br />\n2，老母係咪講真話?尾段張相!同埋諗深一層，領養證可以係偽造。"},{"pid":"c7c69d27f3308c8b49e935a38de5fa6af6c7e2ab","tid":1634574,"uid":77788,"like":17,"dislike":50,"score":-33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:47:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97b17f593bcd603df75a3328d495f44f2889b5de","tid":1634574,"uid":88374,"like":12,"dislike":8,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c7c69d27f3308c8b49e935a38de5fa6af6c7e2ab","tid":1634574,"uid":77788,"like":17,"dislike":50,"score":-33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:47:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:58:58.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"cd334ae9f9e96effe7dc0961ea14a87b106c4fac","tid":1634574,"uid":285514,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:59:37.000Z","msg":"麥當奴叔叔"},{"pid":"14400925b2de74d6f3bfd71d5270fd0db6ba8f52","tid":1634574,"uid":290895,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:29:42.000Z","msg":"華仔吾洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b45877210a5a3bec4ab555b412d5c8929c3a964","tid":1634574,"uid":157510,"like":19,"dislike":98,"score":-79,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://66.media.tumblr.com/910313cb7ab0713e5d50bab573a7f5c7/tumblr_obwohfxou01vs6xh0o1_500.gif\" data-thum